Paper: hep-th/0209174

Date: 2002-09-20

Title: Generalized Weyl systems and kappa-Minkowski space

Authors: Alessandra Agostini, Fedele Lizzi and Alessandro Zampini

Comments: 21 pages, minor corrections and references added

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A17 (2002) 2105-2126

We introduce the notion of generalized Weyl system, and use it to define*-products which generalize the commutation relations of Lie algebras. Inparticular we study in a comparative way various *-products which generalizethe k-Minkowski commutation relations.